{"tid":2492181,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】討論吓喺社會生存嘅智慧","createTime":"2021-04-17T02:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T05:30:11.000Z","uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b585115ce717a0cb932c42d952316b0775a31a0","tid":2492181,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:15:40.000Z","msg":"有錢就係君子，冇錢就係禽獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有錢 == 有 bargaining power，即係佢哋地位高，站喺道德高地之上，其實佢哋講乜都係「啱」，你駁佢就係你哋「錯」<br />\n<br />\n即係話最極端嚟講，只要你冇 bargaining power，即使你點有仁義道德，比你地位 / bargaining power 高嘅對方都可以話你禽獸，而且係「合情合理」<br />\n<br />\n即係一係要有錢，一係要有 bargaining power，如果唔係都係禽獸、小人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5149886700d3d408f574c611d777a8e33361f2","tid":2492181,"uid":213913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:17:03.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a23fc0a8e49216ce0c2ac615e1fe21df19bf7d","tid":2492181,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b585115ce717a0cb932c42d952316b0775a31a0","tid":2492181,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:15:40.000Z","msg":"有錢就係君子，冇錢就係禽獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有錢 == 有 bargaining power，即係佢哋地位高，站喺道德高地之上，其實佢哋講乜都係「啱」，你駁佢就係你哋「錯」<br />\n<br />\n即係話最極端嚟講，只要你冇 bargaining power，即使你點有仁義道德，比你地位 / bargaining power 高嘅對方都可以話你禽獸，而且係「合情合理」<br />\n<br />\n即係一係要有錢，一係要有 bargaining power，如果唔係都係禽獸、小人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"易經第一卦係乾卦，而乾卦第一爻就係講「潛龍勿用」<br />\n<br />\n所以地位低 / 冇錢嗰陣注定俾人踏，𠵱個時候時機未到只可以忍，強出頭反駁只會送死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n形勢比人弱就要忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11addf49b8f999dc723d774e05047dd76845afb","tid":2492181,"uid":25